<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE NEIGHBORHOOD EATERY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JAN JONES 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Henry's Restaurant, 10549 Stanford Ave., Garden Grove. Open Mondays through 
Saturdays from 6 a.m. until between 10 p.m. and 2 a.m., depending on the crowd. 
</P>
<P>
Kitchen closes at 5 p.m. on weekdays and 1 p.m. on Saturdays. (714) 537-9884. A 
tightknit but friendly crowd -- off-duty cops, construction workers, bikers, 
letter carriers from the nearby post office -- gathers for breakfasts, 
blue-plate special lunches, cold beers, retirement parties, you name it. 
Newcomers will feel welcome. JAN JONES 
</P>
</TEXT>
