</P>
<P>
Iraq: 513 
</P>
<P>
Kuwait: 36 
</P>
<P>
Ships: 
</P>
<P>
Iraq: 51 
</P>
<P>
Kuwait: 46 
</P>
<P>
Source: International Institute for Strategic Studies 
</P>
</TEXT>
